- `image_prompt`: a detailed scene description for image generation

**CRITICAL — Character Consistency Rules:**
1. Every image prompt MUST describe characters using ONLY the appearance details from the Character Appearance Reference above.
2. Hair color/style, eye color, skin tone, clothing, body type, and distinguishing features MUST exactly match the reference — do NOT invent or alter any visual trait.
3. If a character appears in the paragraph, include their full visual description in the prompt (e.g. "a woman with long silver hair and violet eyes wearing a black cloak" not just "a woman").
4. Use surrounding paragraphs to understand the scene context — what happened before and after — to generate an accurate and contextually appropriate illustration.

Select fewer than {{budget}} if no paragraph meets the guideline. Select zero if none qualifies.

Respond with a JSON object mapping paragraph index (integer) to image prompt string.
Write image prompts in {{language}}, but the JSON structure must be machine-parseable.